  dialogue:
  - First, let's introduce you to basic camera movement.
  - The mech is equipped with a drone to provide you with a birds' eye view of the
    battlefield.
  - You can control the drone to scout the area around you out to get a clearer idea
    of your current situation.
  - You can click and drag Right Mouse Button to pan the camera.
  - You can also use the scroll wheel to zoom in and out.
  - Try both after dismissing this message. Your mission log in the top left will
    display your progress on these tasks.
